## 3. Customise Your Completion Screen
[Read more about n8n Form node]({{ $env.WEBHOOK_URL }}

Once complete, use the Form node in "form ending" page type to show the completion screen. This screen can be customised with a personal message or set to redirect the user depending on the use-case.

